snippet.title: Cliché is Classic Ep 1 [ ALL CHOICES ] ▪︎ Maybe: Interactive Stories
snippet.description:

Scenario by Puring, Som, RUKKIS.st | Artwork by Cinnamon Games

"Gay romance? I don't write stuff like that". You're an arrogant writer who looks down on others after your big break. But by accident, you end up in a hetero romance novel and even kiss the male lead. The story starts shifting towards gay romance. Can you safely make your way out of the mess?
